text: Larysa Klochkova (born 15 April 1970) is a Ukrainian female Paralympic sitting volleyball player. She is part of the Ukrainian women's national sitting volleyball team. She competed at the 2008 Summer Paralympics, 2012 Summer Paralympics winning the bronze medal, and 2016 Summer Paralympics. == References == Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian sitting volleyball players Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for Ukraine
